    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Puppet Masters who practice the Purple Technique are known as Juggernauts. These shinobi break from the tradition of puppeteering and turn their wondrous Puppet Tools into armor they adorn. </p><p>Some Juggernauts seek to turn their puppet into a machine of death and terror while others become the arbiter of justice and order. Regardless of their goals, these shinobi are bound by one goal: To innovate and become an unstoppable force.</p>",
